<% layout('layouts/infoBoilerplate') -%>

<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-gray-800 pt-20 pb-16 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')]"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-virus text-[#fe424d] mr-3"></i> Safety Tips
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Your safety is our priority. Learn how to travel safely and responsibly with Stayzio.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12">
        <div class="lg:w-1/4 hidden lg:block">
            <div class="sticky top-28 bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)]">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-list text-[#fe424d]"></i> Contents
                </h3>
                <nav class="sticky-nav flex flex-col space-y-1">
                    <a href="#booking-safety" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Booking Safety</a>
                    <a href="#property-safety" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Property Safety</a>
                    <a href="#communication" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Communication</a>
                    <a href="#emergency" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Emergency Info</a>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:w-3/4 prose-content bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)] border border-gray-100">
            
            <div id="booking-safety">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Booking Safety</h2>
                <p>Ensure a secure booking experience by following these essential guidelines:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Always pay through Stayzio:</strong> Never wire money or pay someone directly. If a host asks you to pay off-site, report them immediately.</li>
                    <li><strong>Read reviews carefully:</strong> Check the host's profile and read reviews from previous guests to get an idea of what to expect.</li>
                    <li><strong>Verify listing details:</strong> Make sure the amenities and rules align with your needs before confirming your booking.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div id="property-safety">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-house-user"></i> Property Safety</h2>
                <p>When you arrive at a property, take a moment to familiarize yourself with the surroundings:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Locate all emergency exits, fire extinguishers, and first-aid kits.</li>
                    <li>Check that all doors and windows lock properly.</li>
                    <li>If you notice any safety hazards, contact the host immediately.</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Trust your instincts</h4>
                    <p>If you ever feel unsafe in a property or neighborhood, leave immediately and contact local authorities and Stayzio Support.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="communication">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> Communication</h2>
                <p>Keeping communication on the platform helps us protect you in case issues arise:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Message hosts directly through the Stayzio app to keep a record of your conversation.</li>
                    <li>Do not share your personal phone number or email address until a booking is confirmed.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div id="emergency">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> Emergency Information</h2>
                <p>Always be prepared for an emergency while traveling:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Save local emergency numbers (police, fire, medical) in your phone.</li>
                    <li>Share your itinerary and accommodation details with a trusted friend or family member.</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 mt-6">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Stayzio Emergency Support Line</h4>
                    <p class="mb-1"><strong class="text-gray-900">Phone:</strong> 1-800-STAYZIO-HELP (Available 24/7)</p>
                    <p class="mb-1"><strong class="text-gray-900">Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:safety@stayzio.com" class="text-[#fe424d] hover:underline">safety@stayzio.com</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>